          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-hilary-benn" title="Mr Hilary Benn">Hilary Benn</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I have received no representations about either CDC or Actis in respect of Iraq. There are currently no CDC investments in that country.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_341'>  </a>
