          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gregory-barker" title="Mr Gregory Barker">Gregory Barker</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for International Development what resources CDC/Actis Capital<span class="italic">(a)</span> has directed and <span class="italic">(b)</span> will direct to small and medium enterprises in (i) Iraq and (ii) Afghanistan; and if he will make a statement. [189058]</p>
        </blockquote>
